events.article_title: Introducing PSJ Global(CYCON) on Startup Mining: Stake to Earn Mining Rewards!
events.event_summary: Gate.io introduces the PSJ Global(CYCON) project on its Startup Mining platform. Users can stake CYCON tokens to earn rewards from a total pool of 4,575,592 CYCON, with a prize pool of 27,235.66 CYCON per hour. The staking period runs from October 22 to October 29, 2024.
